<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">I just finally hit level 39, got my new spells and such, and have been at a standstill ever since. My server has a fairly low population of characters around my level that make a good group, and I don't really want to have to just leech xp from higher up guildies, so i've been giving soloing a shot, charm kiting and such, but i've been finding that i'm absolutely terrible at it, and I don't really know what zones are proper for doing as such. If at all possible, it'd be wonderful if any of you could reply back, and give me some tips as how to solo, where are good soloing spots for this level, and anything else that could come in handy. Thanks.
<br />

<br />
Oh, and I don't have LoY, so those are out.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
