<br />

<br />
TD should be alright also when your in low forties to mid.
<br />

<br />
Jaggedpine I loved this place don't worry about faction for killing animals just make sure you kill bandits to make up for it. THis place should be good around mid forties I think to about 50 or 51. Then potemieds should take you a bit farther They immune to run speed changes so good practice. This whole zone is good practice always lots of mobs around and snakes make good pets also. 
<br />

<br />
IF you charm a griff send him into the cave with the gnolls was a zone wide bug about a year ago if you did that, scared the crap outa me  first time I did it. Maybe they fixed it though or maybe not I never did bug it.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
